{"tid":2041621,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲呢兩個星期都因為香港既事好唔開心 好失落","createTime":"2020-05-29T10:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T03:20:39.000Z","uid":92511,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1438c25b6140abc8a54cf32995af2cae7db75d90","tid":2041621,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"自從條垃圾國安法推出至通過後 我都冇一刻係真正開心過<br />\n係唔知點樣可以開心<br />\n香港，一個成長既地方 變到咁樣<br />\n雖然我知道唔係一朝一夕既事 都應該係自23年前就已經決定左係咁樣既結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能自己本身一直都係個熱衷政治 社運既人 由2014開始一直都好投入 但好似愈投入就愈難抽身 更令人心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從一年前就冇真正開心過  應該過心情起伏好大<br />\n都最近 情況更加惡劣 講緊既係聽下網台聽下反送中既歌都會忽然係到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對香港未來擔心 對自己未來擔心 對香港人未來擔心<br />\n一國一制 好似一下子令我地呢班90後冇曬未來<br />\n樓唔會買 小朋友唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要諗走定唔走好 生於斯長於斯死於斯 其實真係好唔想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但男朋友話 我唔走佢唔走 其實佢有份幾好職業 大好前途 <br />\n而我既職業 基本上係國安法一黎就會被封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541c368e41048d6fd9616f5c0433e7988e48a507","tid":2041621,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"無，一樣開心過活"},{"pid":"6edca4ba990fa2f839147928a6d12ee95d39e4d1","tid":2041621,"uid":302204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"you are not alone."},{"pid":"ad6c0d2b46f8c95c3859ae0714e1f83c6b0d6569","tid":2041621,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲想點 大把手足自己一個死撐緊"},{"pid":"a3bfee6550d2b631f85778e5cfe9b0ec2eb39240","tid":2041621,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6c0d2b46f8c95c3859ae0714e1f83c6b0d6569","tid":2041621,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲想點 大把手足自己一個死撐緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"ME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce28ed06e223c1601ba93f7f441ced11140fa95e","tid":2041621,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3bfee6550d2b631f85778e5cfe9b0ec2eb39240","tid":2041621,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6c0d2b46f8c95c3859ae0714e1f83c6b0d6569","tid":2041621,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲想點 大把手足自己一個死撐緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"ME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"加油巴打 u are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df45f99cc11903e2277a8681c2355e6e24e978f8","tid":2041621,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1438c25b6140abc8a54cf32995af2cae7db75d90","tid":2041621,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"自從條垃圾國安法推出至通過後 我都冇一刻係真正開心過<br />\n係唔知點樣可以開心<br />\n香港，一個成長既地方 變到咁樣<br />\n雖然我知道唔係一朝一夕既事 都應該係自23年前就已經決定左係咁樣既結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能自己本身一直都係個熱衷政治 社運既人 由2014開始一直都好投入 但好似愈投入就愈難抽身 更令人心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從一年前就冇真正開心過  應該過心情起伏好大<br />\n都最近 情況更加惡劣 講緊既係聽下網台聽下反送中既歌都會忽然係到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對香港未來擔心 對自己未來擔心 對香港人未來擔心<br />\n一國一制 好似一下子令我地呢班90後冇曬未來<br />\n樓唔會買 小朋友唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要諗走定唔走好 生於斯長於斯死於斯 其實真係好唔想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但男朋友話 我唔走佢唔走 其實佢有份幾好職業 大好前途 <br />\n而我既職業 基本上係國安法一黎就會被封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33JLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e44f934f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}